1 address, and telephone number as well as his or her intention to obtain a new
2 title or salvage title, as applicable, clear of all prior liens, unless the owner or
3 a lienholder objects in writing;
4 (d) More than fourteen (14) days before presenting the affidavit to the county
5 clerk, the affiant had published a legal notice stating his or her intention to
6 obtain title to the vehicle. The legal notice appeared at least twice in a seven
